Nmap is a network exploration tool and security/port scanner.

This plugin provides a simple WebUI to run safe, pre-defined Nmap scans
from OPNsense.

Plugin Changelog
================

1.26

* Simplify scan progress display to a basic running indicator
* Remove live Nmap progress parsing

1.25

* Attach stderr to the pseudo-tty and parse XML output from a temp file

1.24

* Attach Nmap stdin/stdout to a pseudo-tty to enable live stats output

1.23

* Stream Nmap output in unbuffered chunks to capture progress updates

1.22

* Fix progress detection for Nmap "% done" stats lines

1.21

* Force unbuffered progress capture via pseudo-tty

1.20

* Parse progress output even when Nmap uses carriage returns

1.19

* Improve progress parsing for Nmap stats output

1.18

* Use Nmap stats output to show real scan progress
* Display progress in running scan status

1.17

* Add running scans tab with cancel action
* Report when another scan is active before starting a new one

1.16

* Run quick and custom scans in the background to avoid WebUI timeouts
* Show background scan status/output for all scan types
* Extend scan timeout to 10 hours for long-running scans

1.15

* Run interface (host) scans in the background to avoid WebUI timeouts
* Track scan status and show running/last status in the interface results

1.14

* Allow scanning large networks with warnings instead of blocking
* Show scan size warnings in interface scan results
* Fix configd action invocation for scans
* Increase scan timeout to 3600 seconds for long-running scans

1.13

* Fix MAC/vendor parsing for host scans

1.12

* Hide loopback targets from interface scanning and add scan progress indicator

1.11

* Avoid auto-selecting oversized interface networks in host scans

1.10

* Fix host scan updates when profile labels contain spaces

1.9

* Add scan profile management and dynamic profile selection for scans

1.8

* Remove temporary debug output from interfaces endpoint

1.7

* Add MAC/vendor display and improved services formatting in Hosts table
* Improve interface address lookup using physical interface names

1.6

* Fix interface enumeration using config children

1.5

* Add debug interface output for network discovery troubleshooting

1.4

* Improve interface address parsing for zone-indexed IPv6 and hex netmasks

1.3

* Harden interface address parsing for more configd output formats

1.2

* Fix interface network discovery using live interface addresses

1.1

* Add multi-tab UI with network scans, stored host results and custom commands

1.0

* Initial release
